                <note rend="inline" type="source">832.00 Revolutions/129: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul at Porto Alegre</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Nasmith</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1930-10-20T14:00:00-05:00"
                            >October 20, 1930—2 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your October 17th, 4 p.m. On October 18th Secretary of State made statement in
                    his press conference such as you requested.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
